name: complex_if_sub_common_left_factor
section: control-if-arithmetic
args: cond:Bool common:Int a:Int b:Int
type: Bool
expect: True
description: Subtracting an if expression from a common left operand distributes branchwise.
law: (= (fuzz-sub {common} (if {cond} {a} {b})) (if {cond} (fuzz-sub {common} {a}) (fuzz-sub {common} {b})))
